### 📚 Documentation

- correct toml syntax by [@jdx](https://github.com/jdx) in [#5609](https://github.com/jdx/mise/pull/5609)
- removed some markdownlint rules by [@jdx](https://github.com/jdx) in [#5615](https://github.com/jdx/mise/pull/5615)
